  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK575">
<l>kaṇṇiṟ kaṇikalaṅ kaṇṇōṭṭa maḵtiṉṟēl </l>
<l>puṇṇeṉ ṟuṇarap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kind looks are the ornaments of the eyes without these they will be considered (by the wise) to be merely two sores.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
